title: About me
text:
I love cats, a lot. I cannot help myself when they are around. They simply look so cute and I just want to touch their fur!
Sport wise, I have a black belt in Taekwondo, so don’t mess with me :P Recently I just joined a half marathon.
I frequently play the piano. You can check out my humble Youtube channel on the top right corner. I don’t upload a lot of videos by the way. The most recent piece I play is “Story of you” of Alexis Ffrench - a very beautiful and peaceful piece.

title: Hello world!
text:
My name is Trieu and it means tidal waves~
I am a Master’s student at KU Leuven, majoring in International Business Economics and Management.
Having recently moved to Brussels, I am very excited to meet new people and immerse in the European culture.
